Christy Carlson Romano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christy_Carlson_Romano 0 Christy Carlson Romano (born March 20, 1984) is an American actress and singer. She is known for her role as Ren Stevens in the Disney Channel sitcom Even Stevens, and as the voice of the titular character in the Disney Channel animated series Kim Possible.
